General.Name: Western Gold Resources Ltd
General.Description: Western Gold Resources Limited engages in the exploration and extraction of mineral resources. It holds interest in the Wiluna West Gold Project that includes 7 granted mining leases covering an area of 85.8 square kilometers located in Wiluna, Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
